                            </li>
                            <li xml:id="auto_6ecb8igr">
                                <p xml:id="auto_s3pfyyg5">
                                    How many bulbs are still functional after <m>6</m> years?
                                </p>
                            </li>
                        </ol>
                    </p>
                </statement>
            <answer>
                <p xml:id="auto_tm30yw34">
                    <alert>Answers:</alert>
                </p>
                <p xml:id="auto_qrni0evy">
                    <ol xml:id="auto_5to8hjbh" marker="a)">
                        <li xml:id="auto_55kug6tz"><m>100\times(\tfrac{3}{4})^{4} = 100\times\tfrac{81}{256} = \tfrac{8100}{256} \approx 31.64\,\text{(about 32 bulbs)}</m></li>
                        <li xml:id="auto_pbusb6ff"><m>100\times(\tfrac{3}{4})^{6} = 100\times\tfrac{729}{4096} = \tfrac{72900}{4096} \approx 17.79\,\text{(about 18 bulbs)}</m></li>
                    </ol>
